        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p> <b>Defense Language Improvement Act or the DLI Act</b></p> <p>This bill adds authority for the Defense Language Institute to confer a Bachelor of Arts degree in a foreign language&#8212;in addition to the currently authorized Associate degree&#8212;upon a graduate of the Institute's Foreign Language Center.</p>]]>
